0:04:20.860,0:04:24.540
Try to slap three people and see how would you feel.

0:04:24.540,0:04:25.800
You would get tired.

0:04:25.800,0:04:29.280
But you can tap a "trillion" people...

0:04:29.280,0:04:37.360
The SCOAN Sunday Service

